text:
The documentation of mod_proxy shows support for HTTP, FTP and CONNECT porxy 
but doesn't state to which degree this support is given.

It is specially relevant for FTP proxy support, which (as far as I can see), 
doesn't include PUT operations (only GET).

BTW: Where should I suggest FTP proxy PUT support as a new functionality for 
future apache versions?
